<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12057l"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12057l">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12057l"> 57(l)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> meets Declan in Rome / kiss of peace</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">On his arrival at the Eternal City St. Patrick made the acquaintance of <mark>St. Declan</mark>, another Irish missionary, who, with St. Kieran and St. Ailbe, had gone through their course of theological studies <mark>at Rome. They met and parted <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> &lsquo;with the kiss of peace&rsquo;</mark>. <small> William Canon Fleming, <a name="WFSP" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#WFSP"><cite title="source">The Life of St Patrick: Apostle of Ireland</cite></a> (1905) 60</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
